pledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180513/20389303\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180513%2F20389303&d=XeGbOuanAZPJpwXkrA1wSdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=2594351d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180513%2F20389303&h=aa8b62a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180513/20389303</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"相信大家都好關心條撚屌同佢屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:27:29.000Z","msg":"係咪有料爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:07:36.000Z","msg":"應該有啦 <strong></strong>"},{"pid":"134ae85356d1491525eee4b13aff9927e51e2926","tid":663034,"uid":62060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3b9ef05ebcd5815069a2c30857b94c1c9a27767","tid":663034,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebd5d1369704cf59787350f9b9344537ac67e9e1","tid":663034,"uid":57255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"30612b146b20cc63c52fdc929a4d146b5d690411","tid":663034,"uid":135265,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"相信大家都好關心條撚屌同佢屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:27:29.000Z","msg":"係咪有料爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:07:36.000Z","msg":"應該有啦 <strong></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:12:09.000Z","msg":"之前咪爆過一次，有鬼用咩<br />\n香港司法，甚至話所有普通法，都係姑息養奸<br />\n條撚樣唔合作，唔認，請律師，基本上咬佢唔入"},{"pid":"d2f493fdab478e82b37f661c05761cbed5bab9c6","tid":663034,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:32:36.000Z","msg":"快啲好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgm